    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "I was thinking of something more specific (and simpler to use because of that) like `WithDamagedAnimation/Overlay`, but that could also work.\nDepends on how we do other damage-induced changes like reduced speed and such. If we go for upgrades on low health (either on DamageState change or on HP < X%), then `WithDecoration` might be the obvious choice. If not, these traits can directly implement `INotifyDamageStateChanged` and do their thing quite easily.\n"
  },
