    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Damaged decorations can now be done using conditions and With* traits, so this ticket can now cover adding the flame overlays to the mods.  This would be best done with a new trait that specifies a list of valid WVec positions and a list of sequences that can be drawn at them.  A subset can then be drawn at any time while the trait is active."
